--LDA- RR XX I ADRES
=> Load register with the address 

IR = 000001 RR XX I ADRES
PC = current location


if(I==0)
	{
	if(X=x0)
		{ EA=Address }
	if(x=x1,x2,x3)
		{ EA=Address + [Xx] }
	}
	
if(I==1)
	{
	if(X=x0)
		{ EA=[Address] }
	if(x=x1,x2,x3)
		{ EA=[Address + [Xx] ] }
	}

MAR=EA
MDR=[EA]
RR=MAR
 
 

Example :- 
LDA R0 0 25  
-> Load R0 with contents of '25'
	
	START
	Display current value of PC 
	Update IR 
	I=0;
	X=0;
	EA=25
	MAR=25
	MDR=[25]
	R0=25 
	END 